If brightness in ubuntu is not working you can do following changes in grub:
1.Open '/etc/default/grub' file using gedit or any other text editor
2.Find the line given as below :
  GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="quiet splash"
3.Change above line to:
  GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="quiet splash acpi_backlight=vendor"
